OL,3,C'No place for racism': Three schools
OL,4,Crecord 78 exclusions for racist abuse
OL,6,FThree state secondary schools in
OL,7,FJersey, Haute Vallee, Grainville and
OL,8,FLe Rocquier, have the highest number
OL,9,Fof suspensions linked to racist abuse
OL,10,Fon the island.
OL,12,FIn data obtained through a Freedom of
OL,13,FInformation (FOI) request by ITV News,
OL,14,Fthese three schools recorded a total
OL,15,Fof 78 incidents of suspensions for
OL,16,Fracist abuse from the academic years
OL,17,Fbetween 2018 to 2025.
