OL,3,C'No place for racism': Three schools
OL,4,Crecord 78 exclusions for racist abuse
OL,6,FTwo St Helier schools accounted for
OL,7,Fthe highest numbers, with a total of
OL,8,F34 exclusions linked to racist abuse
OL,9,Fat Haute Vallee and 28 at Grainville.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, Le Rocquier, in the parish
OL,12,Fof St Clement, recorded 16 incidents.
OL,14,FThere were six incidents at both Les
OL,15,FQuennevais and Victoria College, and
OL,16,Ffewer than five incidents at Hautlieu,
OL,17,FJanvrin and St Saviours.
OL,19,FState schools that had no recorded
OL,20,Fexclusions linked to racist abuse were
OL,21,Fnot listed in the data.
