OL,3,C'No place for racism': Three schools
OL,4,Crecord 78 exclusions for racist abuse
OL,6,FBeatriz Poree, Deputy of St Helier
OL,7,FSouth, told ITV News she's deeply
OL,8,F"saddened" by the findings.
OL,10,FShe added: "There's no time and place
OL,11,Fanymore in our society for racist
OL,12,Fbehaviour, which we know is a learned
OL,13,Fbehaviour".
OL,15,FShe also said it's "not surprising"
OL,16,Fthat two St Helier schools recorded
OL,17,Fthe highest number of incidents.
