OL,6,F"It's not incidental - we know that
OL,7,Fthe majority of migrant workers tend
OL,8,Fto settle in St Helier, so you have a
OL,9,Fmuch greater mix of people who come
OL,10,Ffrom different nationalities".
OL,12,FIn a separate FOI request submitted by
OL,13,FITV News earlier this year, it was
OL,14,Frevealed that the number of exclusions
OL,15,Ffor children being racist in
OL,16,FGovernment of Jersey schools has more
OL,17,Fthan doubled in two academic years.
