OL,3,C'No place for racism': Three schools
OL,4,Crecord 78 exclusions for racist abuse
OL,6,FA total of 27 instances of racist
OL,7,Fabuse led to student suspensions
OL,8,Facross 2024 to 2025 - compared to 12
OL,9,Fin 2022-23.
OL,11,FRegarding the apparent rise in racism
OL,12,Fin schools, the Reform Jersey
OL,13,Fpolitician said it's likely due to a
OL,14,Fgreater number of people "coming to
OL,15,FJersey from different cultural groups
OL,16,Fand languages", which has increased in
OL,17,Fthe past five years.
OL,19,FDeputy Poree added that the government
OL,20,Fand schools need to work together to
OL,21,Fstamp out racism from an early age.
