OL,4,Crecord 78 exclusions for racist abuse
OL,6,F"We take this very seriously. While
OL,7,Fthe rise in suspensions is concerning,
OL,8,Fit shows schools are taking decisive
OL,9,Faction and it is also due to a more
OL,10,Faccurate system of reporting
OL,11,Fsuspensions.
OL,13,F"Any incident is one too many and we
OL,14,Fare committed to tackling racial abuse
OL,15,Fwith mandatory policies, staff
OL,16,Ftraining and education, to ensure
OL,17,Fevery child can learn and thrive in an
OL,18,Finclusive and respectful environment.
